# @aai-agency/og-components Rules

## Code Style

- Arrow functions only: `const foo = () => {}`, never `function foo() {}`
- Biome for formatting: `pnpm lint`
- TypeScript strict mode, no `any`
- ESM only

## Component Conventions

- Tailwind CSS with shadcn tokens (bg-background, text-foreground, border-border)
- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for conditional class merging
- Every interactive control needs a `<Tooltip>` wrapper
- All panels use solid white backgrounds, no transparency
- Selected markers keep original fill color with dark border

## Data

- Every Asset needs: id, name, type, status, coordinates, properties
- Domain fields (operator, cumOil) go in `properties`, not top-level
- Use Zod schemas at data boundaries
- TimeSeries: `{ id, fluidType, curveType, unit, frequency, data: DataPoint[] }`

## Map Component

- Requires `mapboxAccessToken` prop (from env var, never hardcoded)
- Needs `<TooltipProvider>` ancestor
- Uses mapbox-gl directly, not react-map-gl
- XState machine manages all map interactions

## Charts

- Both LineChart and ProductionChart use `TimeSeries[]`
- Require `import "uplot/dist/uPlot.min.css"`
- Need explicit container height

## Files

- Components: `[feature].comp.tsx` or `[feature].tsx`
- Types: `[feature].types.ts`
- Tests colocated: `__tests__/[feature].test.ts`
